---
import DefaultLayout from '../../layouts/DefaultLayout.astro'

export async function getStaticPaths({ paginate }) {
  return paginate([], { pageSize: 1 })
}

const { page } = Astro.props
---

<DefaultLayout
  title="About Us"
  description="Learn more about The Francis Bacon Debate Society, our mission, history, and team."
>
  <section class="my-12">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Membership</h1>
      <p class="text-lg mb-6">
        Membership of the White’s Club is not currently being offered and the waiting list for new members is now closed, subject to annual review.
      <p class="text-lg mb-6">
        Candidates already on the waiting list may use the Club’s Dining Room.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg mb-6">
        For more information please contact the Membership Office by email: membership@thewhitesclub.com
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="my-12 py-12">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Leadership Team</h2>
      <p class="text-lg mb-6">
        Meet the distinguished individuals who lead The Francis Bacon Debate Society with passion and dedication:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-none pl-0">
        <li class="mb-8 flex items-center">
          <img src="/images/jane-doe.jpg" alt="Jane Doe" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full mr-4">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Jane Doe</h3>
            <p class="text-md"><strong>President:</strong> An experienced debater with a background in political science, Jane has been leading the club with enthusiasm and dedication for the past three years.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="mb-8 flex items-center">
          <img src="/images/john-smith.jpg" alt="John Smith" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full mr-4">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">John Smith</h3>
            <p class="text-md"><strong>Vice President:</strong> With a passion for public speaking and a knack for organising events, John supports the club's activities and helps mentor new members.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="mb-8 flex items-center">
          <img src="/images/emily-johnson.jpg" alt="Emily Johnson" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full mr-4">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Emily Johnson</h3>
            <p class="text-md"><strong>Secretary:</strong> Emily ensures that all club meetings and events are well-documented and communicated to members. Her attention to detail keeps the club running smoothly.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="my-12 py-12">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our History</h2>
    <p class="text-lg mb-6">
      Founded in the year 2024, The Francis Bacon Debate Society stands as a beacon of intellectual discourse and the free exchange of ideas. Our society is dedicated to fostering a culture of rigorous debate, critical thinking, and eloquent expression.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg mb-6">
      At the heart of our society lies a commitment to the highest values in debating. We believe that through respectful and informed debate, individuals can broaden their perspectives, challenge their preconceptions, and contribute to the collective wisdom of our community.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg mb-6">
      Our members are encouraged to engage in thoughtful discussions on a wide range of topics, from contemporary issues to timeless philosophical questions. We uphold the principles of integrity, respect, and intellectual curiosity in all our endeavours.
    </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</DefaultLayout>

<style lang="scss">
.container {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 1rem;
}

.bg-gray-100 {
  background-color: #f7fafc;
}

.text-4xl {
  font-size: 2.25rem;
}

.text-3xl {
  font-size: 1.875rem;
}

.text-xl {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
}

.text-lg {
  font-size: 1.125rem;
}

.font-bold {
  font-weight: 700;
}

.mb-6 {
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.mb-8 {
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.my-12 {
  margin-top: 3rem;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
}

.w-24 {
  width: 6rem;
}

.h-24 {
  height: 6rem;
}

.rounded-full {
  border-radius: 9999px;
}

.mr-4 {
  margin-right: 1rem;
}

.flex {
  display: flex;
}

.items-center {
  align-items: center;
}
</style>